BlackRock’s Cavatoni to Head Americas Capital Markets at iShares

-- B y   B e i   H u
-- 
2011-10-19T10:58:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/blackrock-s-cavatoni-to-head-americas-capital-markets-at-ishares.html
BlackRock Inc. (BLK) , the world’s largest
asset manager, named Joe Cavatoni to head Americas  Capital
Markets  for its iShares unit.  Cavatoni aims to be in New York full time by the end of the
year and BlackRock is currently in the process of identifying a
successor for him in  Asia , according to an e-mailed statement by
Fiona Tyndall, a spokeswoman for the asset manager.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bei Hu in Hong Kong at 
 bhu5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christian Baumgaertel at 
 cbaumgaertel@bloomberg.net  